{"id":"812793695917211648","type":"text","timestamp":1775140472,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812793695917211648","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://creatingblackcharacters.tumblr.com/post/811561995240407040/i-love-how-unapologetic-he-is-and-rightfully-so\">creatingblackcharacters</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://bogleech.tumblr.com/post/811542004233338880/havent-seen-a-lot-about-this-on-tumblr-so-maybe\">bogleech</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://croaksac.tumblr.com/post/811478497674543104/the-complete-and-total-defeat-in-the-lawyers\">croaksac</a>:</p><blockquote><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1920\" data-orig-width=\"1080\" data-npf='{\"type\":\"video\",\"provider\":\"tumblr\",\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_tc4j97lOwv1qfw1tv_720.mp4\",\"media\":{\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_tc4j97lOwv1qfw1tv_720.mp4\",\"type\":\"video/mp4\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":1920},\"poster\":[{\"media_key\":\"7f24a651f9f745b3e1b2f3caa4face85:ea82f9ea2ae1e576-ff\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"width\":456,\"height\":810,\"url\":\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7f24a651f9f745b3e1b2f3caa4face85/ea82f9ea2ae1e576-ff/s540x810/0d7ca0a8736552a210eadf57a2b2020d82a62f8e.jpg\"}]}'><video controls=\"controls\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" playsinline=\"playsinline\" muted=\"muted\" poster=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7f24a651f9f745b3e1b2f3caa4face85/ea82f9ea2ae1e576-ff/s540x810/0d7ca0a8736552a210eadf57a2b2020d82a62f8e.jpg\"><source src=\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_tc4j97lOwv1qfw1tv_720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></source></video></figure><p>the complete and total defeat in the prosecutor&rsquo;s voice at the very end&hellip;.. im 💀💀💀</p></blockquote><p>Havent seen a lot about this on tumblr so maybe not a lot of people know:</p><ul><li>He was wrongfully raided by police in 2022</li><li>He used footage and names of the specific cops in posts, videos and songs making fun of them</li><li>The cops sued for defamation and cried in court about the songs ruining their lives</li><li>He won anyway</li></ul></blockquote><p>I love how unapologetic he is. And rightfully so!! How you gone cry about being embarrassed when you weren&rsquo;t crying about barging into my home and threatening my life? No one was worried about anybody&rsquo;s children when they weren&rsquo;t the right color. They good. 🤷🏾‍♀️</p></blockquote>","source_url":"https://youtube.com/shorts/2m8NpGplUOM","source_title":"youtube.com","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"croaksac","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":540,"header_full_height":304,"avatar_shape":"circle","background_color":"#FFB5E4","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/83bf9bc40f25ffb5334018340ec3d5c9/2922129c6a3002a6-b3/s540x304/12cfade6c6dff81c39c2883bb43559171ddecd6f.gif","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/83bf9bc40f25ffb5334018340ec3d5c9/2922129c6a3002a6-b3/s2048x3072/3d10dd7214ffdbb201fdea5e3cdfb0a2e8a71634.gif","header_image_poster":"https://44.media.tumblr.com/83bf9bc40f25ffb5334018340ec3d5c9/2922129c6a3002a6-b3/s2048x3072_f1/0c1fcffd287e75e10447ff2b42bbd9a95461b128.gif","header_image_scaled":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/83bf9bc40f25ffb5334018340ec3d5c9/2922129c6a3002a6-b3/s2048x3072/3d10dd7214ffdbb201fdea5e3cdfb0a2e8a71634.gif","header_stretch":true,"link_color":"#e5529e","show_avatar":true,"show_description":true,"show_header_image":true,"show_title":true,"title_color":"#444444","title_font":"Sans Serif","title_font_weight":"bold"},"share_likes":false,"share_following":false,"can_be_followed":true},"post":{"id":"811478497674543104"},"content_raw":"<p><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1920\" data-orig-width=\"1080\" data-npf='{\"type\":\"video\",\"provider\":\"tumblr\",\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_tc4j97lOwv1qfw1tv_720.mp4\",\"me